        "content": "<p><code>until</code> seems to be some sort of a reserved word in lean 4, but I am unable to find it in the documentation. I am just curious because I did something like the following</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">until</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>but got <code>unexpected token 'until'; expected identifier</code>.</p>",
        "id": 504070912,
        "sender_full_name": "Mrigank Pawagi",
        "timestamp": 1741346666
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=Lean.doElemRepeat__Until_#doc\">docs#Lean.doElemRepeat__Until_</a></p>",
        "id": 504072473,
        "sender_full_name": "Aaron Liu",
        "timestamp": 1741347152
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Thanks! This line in the code makes it clear:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">syntax</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"repeat \"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">doSeq</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ppDedent</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">ppLine</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"until \"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">term</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">doElem</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>I have used <code>repeat</code> but not <code>repeat ... until</code>.</p>",
        "id": 504072833,
        "sender_full_name": "Mrigank Pawagi",
        "timestamp": 1741347271
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>In case it is helpful for some other time, you could also have found out about this as follows:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Mathlib</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Tactic</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">FindSyntax</span>\n\n<span class=\"sd\">/--</span>\n<span class=\"sd\">info: Found 1 use among 579 syntax declarations</span>\n<span class=\"sd\">In `Init.While`:</span>\n<span class=\"sd\">  Lean.doElemRepeat__Until_: 'repeat  _ until'</span>\n<span class=\"sd\">-/</span>\n<span class=\"bp\">#</span><span class=\"n\">guard_msgs</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">in</span>\n<span class=\"bp\">#</span><span class=\"n\">find_syntax</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"until\"</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
